{
  "stem": "4967.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he became chief electrician for Messerschmitt factory in Germany there in Kaufering.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He had better facilities.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what was the factory he's to start from scratch, to build a factory, to manufacture Messerschmitt planes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I actually got a job to work in-- in the camp in this-- in this [GERMAN] camp number one to look as a-- as a messenger boy, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to be a messenger between the Germans officers, which was outside the camp, and the internal camp in-- in the camp, officers in the camp.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] First of all, as we came there, we find-- we find in the camp was another camp inside our camp, a woman's camp from Lithuanian woman and Hungarian woman.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You didn't know if they're women or they're men.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everybody had shaved heads.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And women who have been in the camps became flatchested-- put it nicely.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I-- we were five children in this camp, three Lithuanian boys, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] which I met them after the war.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And actually, two of them I met in New York when I've been.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the women felt sorry for me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They used to give me bread, extra plate of soup-- plate, I didn't have a plate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I had a metal tin from-- from something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We got parcles from Red Cross a week later.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And in these parcels was tins of meat, milk, cheese.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And straight away, we start to do things with them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The Germans didn't supply us any utensils even to get the black coffee, the imitation coffee.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And this we used to call a [NON-ENGLISH] where you keep your soup, your this, everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
